<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="the-moment-that">the moment (that)</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1as-soon-as">1.<strong>[引导时间状语从句，相当于连词as soon as] 一… (就…)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Alisha fell asleep the moment she got into bed. 
艾丽莎一上床就睡着了。</p><footer>译林⑦ – 3</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Be careful! The machine starts the moment you press the button.  
小心！这台机器一按按钮就会启动。</p><footer>2011 湖北</footer></div></div>